{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_50043.jpg","bgm":"bgm23_tokime05","nameNarration":"Chiharu","narration":"We suddenly got a phone call while I was watching TV.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_50013.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"We arrived at Tokime Village without any explanation, @and I was suddenly asked to offer up my soul. @Both my mom and I were bewildered..."},{"narration":"But now, I've already made up my mind."},{"narration":"Because I met Shizuka and Sunao, @heard about what Diviners are from them, @and saw how they actually fight.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_50023.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"Because I'd always wanted to be a hero @who could help somebody else. @And now, I was sure that it'd come true."},{"narration":"I know what I'm going to wish @for with this divine power.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_50033.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"I'm gonna punish those bad people in the police, @who've been ruining the heroes I looked up to."},{"narration":"Because― like Granny said too― @that's what will protect people, @and make the whole country better."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102601,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narration":"And I was even praised by Shizuka's mother. @She said I had enough courage, and to be confident in myself. @So I'm going to become a Diviner.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_50043.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"To accept this bizarre truth, @just like Kouichi Todoroki said..."},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Chiharu","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","nameRight":"Sunao","textLeft":"...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":800600,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Chiharu's Mother","nameRight":"Shizuka's Mother","textLeft":"...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":801000,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102601,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Chiharu","textCenter":"(It was bustling until just now, but everybody's gone quiet...)","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(It's like when we went to my grandpa's funeral back then...)"},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"(Ah—... What am I even thinking about...?)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102601,"pos":2}],"textClear":1,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":801800,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Mikoshiba","nameRight":"Chiharu","textLeft":"Chiharu."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102601,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Ye, yes."},{"chara":[{"id":801800}],"textLeft":"Go to the front of the stage."},{"chara":[{"id":102601}],"textRight":"Yes..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51068_storyselect_tokime/memoria_1388_1.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Chiharu","narration":"―Chiharu―@(It all feels so grave now...)","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":35.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@(Did I really just lose to my curiosity...?)"},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@(Or was I deceived by how cheerful everyone was...?)"},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@..."},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@Mom..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51068_storyselect_tokime/memoria_1388_1.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":800600,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Chiharu's Mother","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51068_storyselect_tokime/memoria_1388_1.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Chiharu","narration":"―Chiharu―@(No... It'll be alright...)","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":35.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@(Because I'm much more worried@about my mom than about myself.)"},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@(But my mom...)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51068_storyselect_tokime/memoria_1388_1.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21443.jpg","chara":[{"id":800600}],"nameCenter":"Chiharu's Mother","textCenter":"It's okay. I already heard it from Lady Mikoshiba, @so I've braced myself for whatever happens...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51068_storyselect_tokime/memoria_1388_1.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameNarration":"Chiharu","narration":"―Chiharu―@(That's what she said...)","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":35.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"―Chiharu―@(So calm down, and have confidence in yourself...)"},{"bgm":"stop","nameNarration":"Mikoshiba","narration":"―Mikoshiba―@Now..."},{"narration":"―Mikoshiba―@We shall commence the Kagura of the Nation's Guard,@and with it, the Diviner's Ceremony."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51068_storyselect_tokime/memoria_1388_1.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
